    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Land which has been provided with water systems, sewers, sidewalks, and other basic facilities in preparation for residential or industrial development.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
